reviewText: My favorite spinning DVD from the ones I have

I love the workout on this video.  It is my first "rides" dvd and I love the countdown timer that let's you know how much time is left on each seated/standing climb, etc.  I think it is a great workout so I will buy more of these dvds.
This is one of the top Spinning videos out there. Great coaching  and information to follow on the screen. Music in the back ground is upbeat
